snippet.title: Their Eyes trailer
snippet.description:
This is my first game as a (noob) indie dev. :D
"Their Eyes" is a short lovecraftian adventure for Mac & Windows.

The full game is downloadable for free on itch.io:
https://black-and-noir.itch.io/their-eyes
___
Read more on Free Game Planet:
https://www.freegameplanet.com/their-eyes-downloadable-game
___
The beautiful font m5x7 was created by Daniel Linssen:
https://managore.itch.io
